doasedit(8)

NAME
    doasedit - simple sudoedit alternative for doas.

SYNOPSIS
    doasedit file

DESCRIPTION
    doasedit allows a permitted user to edit file as the superuser.

INSTALLATION
    Globally (for all users):

        # curl -L http://git.io/doasedit.raw | doas tee /usr/local/bin/doasedit
        # chmod +x /usr/local/bin/doasedit

EXAMPLES
    To run an editor as root:

        $ doasedit /etc/doas.conf

